[preface]
== Dedication

This book is dedicated to you, the general public. People whom I have never met. Thank you for saving me. New Democracy is my galaxy size attempt to repay what I received. 

 I thought I was going to die every day growing up. Grade school changed that for me. My teachers cared about me. I recieved not only a free education, but a safe place away from my parents.

I moved out of the house at age 17 and then I moved out of Indiana to California at age 23. In the 1980s community college was free in California except books and parking. Then I transfered to UC Berkeley. There I received free undergrad and graduate education based upon my academic performance.

You invested in me, saved me as a child. New Democracy is my attempt to save you by saving Democracy.  I have spent my entire life responding in kind with what was received from you. 

Enjoy!